imdb.plot outline: What's your fashion status? Think it's time to update your profile pic? Model, make-up artist and today's "it" girl Solenn Heussaff will transform the life of a plain Jane or Joe every week in her newest makeover show, Fashbook. Solenn will be working with an expert make-over team composed of face and hair master Jigs Mayuga, style diva Eric Poliquit and life coach Miss A.
